</a>
<a class="twitter" target="_blank" 
    href="https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?url=/{?twitter}twitter{:else}web{/twitter}#{name}&text=Congrats {name} for being named one of @thedailybeast's %23beastBest {?twitter}Twitter accounts{:else}websites{/twitter}!&via=thedailybeast&hashtags=beastBest&related=Newsweek&counturl={url}">
    <span class="icon-twitter" aria-hidden="true"></span>
</a>